source.sqlReaderQuery:
select  * from dbo.GD_PRODUCT_MAIN where product_main_id in (
select distinct f_product_main_item from dbo.gx_national_assortment)
and upper(status)='DELETED'

select CASE
        WHEN upper(status) = 'DELETED' THEN
            -- If the ID contains an underscore, extract the part before it
            CASE
                WHEN CHARINDEX('_', id) > 0 THEN LEFT(id, CHARINDEX('_', id) - 1)
                ELSE id -- If no underscore, return the entire ID
            END
        ELSE id -- For non-deleted statuses, return the original ID
    END AS
